The,TomTom,Online,Routing,API,is,a,navigation,solution,for,travel,routes,and,destinations,The,API,provides,calculations,of,route,distances,and,travel,time,estimates,relative,to,the,prevailing,traffic,conditions,and,prescribed,road,speeds,of,the,preferred,routes,It,also,displays,geometric,route,definitions,in,addition,to,showing,the,sequence,of,waypoints,or,turns,according,to,the,selections,of,users,The,API,sends,requests,in,HTTP,format,and,returns,responses,in,JSON,JSONP,or,XML,format